history.content:
Historically this has taken until October to update, so no need to worry.  I would give it another month, as you don't really need this updated until senior year.

You could open a case with Cal Student Central (online or 120 Sproul), but I think it would be easiest to just submit another official transcript to Cal (in a sealed envelope).

Hi, I'm a freshman with course credit from a community college (fulfilling an L&S breadth requirement), and I still have a notice on my Calcentral feed that UCB has not received a transcript from Foothill College. Who should I talk to/what should I do to sort this issue out? Thank you!
